{"tid":672473,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Amd  zen 2   猜測","createTime":"2018-05-21T04:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T09:40:21.000Z","uid":58882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6879b6d8acd5fa56cbd92448254deb2c26d738d5","tid":672473,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"關於zen2的第一個chip，rome到底是什麼樣子的，有以下幾個比較公認的猜測：<br />\n1. 2019年的上半年，Rome會發布<br />\n2. 7nm, mcm設計<br />\n3. 採用TSMC的7nm<br />\n<br />\n其中有幾個沒有被廣泛認可的猜測：<br />\n1.CONARDPC說的，64core，128thread， 256MB L3 cache<br />\n2.AdoredTV說的，zen2有5個die，其中一個die是沒有cpu core的--- 從上面視頻16分鐘開始看。<br />\n<br />\n重點分析下AdoredTV說的那個沒核心的die，按他的說法，這個die集成內存控制器和IF等部件，負責整個CPU的輸入輸出。所以zen2的設計是4個CCX加一個IOchip。假定這個是準確的，可以分析一下製程問題了：<br />\n1. ccx肯定是TSMC的7nm，這個基本沒有疑問，gf的進度落後tsmc很多，工藝也無法相提並論。<br />\n2.重點在這個iochip，是tsmc嗎？是7nm嗎？<br />\n3.WSA的問題怎麼辦？如果rome完全由tsmc製造，wsa的問題怎麼處理？一年從GF買的芯片無法達到一定量，AMD是要交罰款的，而且不是小數目。<br />\n<br />\n所以有以下幾種可能：<br />\n1. 全部TSMC造，拼起來。 ryzen3交給gf去做，這樣wsa的問題不大，但是桌面要求高頻高性能，gf能滿足嗎？大大的問號。<br />\n2. TSMC造ccx， GF造iochip。這樣的話，一個rome或者ryzen3裡面就含有兩家廠的chip，wsa天然滿足，amd不用交任何罰款，同時產能也可以得到進一步的保證。不過問題又來了，iochip讓GF造，如果7nm的話，進度能趕上？有沒有可能不用7nm？<br />\n3. gf造rome，tsmc造ryzen3. 可能性低，道理同上，gf的製程和tsmc沒辦法相提並論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource link : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ucMQermB9wQ&amp;t=171s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DucMQermB9wQ%26t%3D171s&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7a704e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ucMQermB9wQ&amp;t=171s</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chiphell.com/thread-1855408-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chiphell.com%2Fthread-1855408-1-1.html&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=5fa1a9d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chiphell.com/thread-1855408-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"75e51594c84f7a658e01fe99ce0015583677d2ab","tid":672473,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"0eda44df82079db86ba24d88cc784db5da6ea4e3","tid":672473,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:16:03.000Z","msg":"女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f362aacd9f49c17a260fe334213bf2793d0ea11","tid":672473,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0eda44df82079db86ba24d88cc784db5da6ea4e3","tid":672473,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:16:03.000Z","msg":"女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:17:48.000Z","msg":"gf坑amd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2442ec8a1e851e2ac3b82c77672b0c8db03bfbc","tid":672473,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"gf 放棄左10nm, 都唔夠tsmc黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外4個ccx, 即係16core<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c28e971f22f5b6c3e3f2b6fa9511bb34b2155f","tid":672473,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"2.重點在這個iochip，是tsmc嗎？是7nm嗎？<br />\n<br />\n唔係用同一個技術個頻sync唔到<br />\nasync的話好難搞"},{"pid":"ce6ef34e601a8daa3b92b910f30341efdecdfc30","tid":672473,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2442ec8a1e851e2ac3b82c77672b0c8db03bfbc","tid":672473,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"gf 放棄左10nm, 都唔夠tsmc黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外4個ccx, 即係16core<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /